item.title: CVE-2021-21597|2024-08-03T18:16:23.640Z -- dell -- wyse%20thinos
item.description: Dell Wyse ThinOS, version 9.0, contains a Sensitive Information Disclosure Vulnerability. An authenticated malicious user with physical access to the system could exploit this vulnerability to read sensitive information written to the log files.

item.title: CVE-2021-21598|2024-08-03T18:16:23.806Z -- dell -- wyse%20thinos
item.description: Dell Wyse ThinOS, versions 9.0, 9.1, and 9.1 MR1, contain a Sensitive Information Disclosure Vulnerability. An authenticated attacker with physical access to the system could exploit this vulnerability to read sensitive Smartcard data in log files.
